WEBVTT

00:00:01.146 --> 00:00:03.944
There is something we desperately need

00:00:03.968 --> 00:00:06.888
that we cannot stop doing:

00:00:06.912 --> 00:00:08.078
it is breathing.

00:00:08.596 --> 00:00:10.210
Do you want to try?

00:00:10.234 --> 00:00:13.002
Why don't we stop breathing together

00:00:13.026 --> 00:00:16.182
for, let's say, even 10 seconds.

00:00:16.206 --> 00:00:17.364
Is that OK?

00:00:17.388 --> 00:00:18.825
Let's do it.

00:00:18.849 --> 00:00:21.421
Get ready ... OK, now!